        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;No Patient Left Alone Act of &lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires hospitals, as a condition of Medicare participation, to have certain written policies and procedures that provide for patient visitation rights and to inform patients of such rights, including any applicable restrictions.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
